Koui: Minamoto no Hisako (源久子)
Koui: Fujiwara no Shizuko (藤原静子)
Court lady: A daughter of Fujiwara no Tsugukage, "Ise" (伊勢) (875/7–ca. 939)
Court lady: Fujiwara no "Hōshi" (藤原褒子), daughter of Fujiwara no Tokihira
(from unknown women)
 

